-> Setup homebrew
brew install gcc
/opt/homebrew/bin
ls
g++ --version
sudo rm g++
ln -s g++-14 g++
(post this restart the terminal)
g++ --version
g++-14 --version
ls -ltrh
which g++-14
which g++
sudo ln -s /opt/homebrew/opt/gcc/bin/g++-14  /usr/local/bin/g++


-> Add this flag to C++ Single File
-std=c++17 add in c++ build file

-> Also add the below flags in .zshrc and source it and then restart sublime:
export CPATH=/opt/homebrew/include
export LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/homebrew/lib
